1. *Crni* vuk je prošao kroz šumu. (The black wolf went through the forest.)
2. Ona je nosila *crnu* haljinu. (She was wearing a black dress.)
3. *Crnilo* je toliko tamno da se ništa nije videlo. (The darkness was so dark that nothing could be seen.)
4. Bezbojne boje su postale *crne*. (The colorless colors became black.)
5. *Crne* magije su prisutne u našem gradu. (Black magic is present in our town.)
6. Ona je imala *crne* oči. (She had black eyes.)